         <div type="edition" xml:lang="kan-Latn">
             <p>
                 <lb n="1"/>śrī svasti samadhi-gata-pañca-mahā-sabda-mahā
                 <lb n="2" break="no"/><supplied reason="undefined">sā</supplied>maṁtādhi-pati sāhasa-rudraṁ <gap reason="undefined" quantity="2" unit="character" precision="low"/> krānta-nārāyaṇa vivēka-kama
                 <lb n="3" break="no"/><supplied reason="undefined">ḷā</supplied>sanaṁ saṁgrāma-mārttāṇḍa-pratāpa-diḷīpaṁ raṇa-raṁga-rāghavaṁ
                 <lb n="4"/>dharmma-dharmātmajaṁ <gap reason="undefined" quantity="5" unit="character" precision="low"/> vikrāntēyaṁ śauca-pavanā
                 <lb n="5" break="no"/>tmajaṁ satya-rādhēyaṁ bhōga-kusumāyudhaṁ vairībha-ka
                 <lb n="6" break="no"/>ṇṭhīravaṁ vīra-cūḍāmaṇi <gap reason="undefined" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/> māṇikyaṁ tailana cakraṁ
                 <lb n="7"/>bhuvanaika-malla śrīmad-āhavamalla pāda-paṁkaja-brahma
                 <lb n="8" break="no"/>raṁ śrīmad-daśavarmma-dēvara śrī-pāda-padmōpajīvigaḷ</p>
             <p>
                 <lb n="9"/><supplied reason="undefined">ḷ</supplied>appa rāja-sāmyada perggaḍe <supplied reason="undefined">daḷā</supplied>payya pramukha-karaṇamuṁ
                 <lb n="10"/><supplied reason="undefined">ma</supplied>neya verggaḍe goṇayya pramukha-karaṇamuṁ pēṟe <supplied reason="undefined">Avar’ a</supplied>numata
                 <lb n="11" break="no"/>doḷ</p>
             
             <p> śaka-varṣa 918<supplied reason="undefined">ne</supplied>ya durmmukhi samvatsarada śrāvaṇa bahuḷa 1
                 <lb n="12"/>sōmavāra karaṁjōḷada ūroḍeya kēsavayyaṁge saṁ <gap reason="undefined" quantity="2" unit="character" precision="low"/>
                 <lb n="13" break="no"/>yya koṭṭa saṁsthā-patrav' ent' andoḍe</p> 
                 
             <p> manmatha-saṁvatsarado<supplied reason="undefined">ḷu</supplied>
                 <lb n="14"/>bīja-biḻda utta<supplied reason="undefined">ma</supplied> kariya nelakke salikke madhyamakke
                 <lb n="15"/>salike 1 paṇa 3 kaniṣthakke salike 1 uṟkege uḻta <gap reason="undefined" quantity="1" unit="character" precision="low"/>
                 <lb n="16"/><gap reason="undefined" quantity="2" unit="character" precision="low"/> pēḷda maryyāde baḻikaṁ varṣaṁ-prati</p> 
             
             <p> uttama ne
                 <lb n="17" break="no"/>lakke paṅa 2 madhyakke paṇa 1 aḍḍa 1 kaniṣṭha
                 <lb n="18" break="no"/>kke paṇa 1 baḻivamārge 7 barisado <gap reason="undefined" quantity="1" unit="character" precision="low"/>
                 <lb n="19"/>nilkaṁ irkkaṇna maryādege vyavasthe <gap reason="undefined" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/>
                 <lb n="20"/>lla bareda madhusū<supplied reason="undefined">dana</supplied> <gap reason="undefined" quantity="3" unit="character" precision="low"/>
             </p>
             
            
